\contentsline {table}{\numberline {\relax Table\nobreakspace {\relax 2}.1}{\ignorespaces Complexity and approximation landscape for Non-Conjecturing PPI MATP. ``Latent $\delta ^*$'' indicates the general case with unique but unknown dependencies. ``LPT'' is Longest Processing Time first; ``RLS'' is Reactive List Scheduling (Thm.\nobreakspace {}\ref {thm:rls-approx}); ``LST'' is Lenstra--Shmoys--Tardos LP rounding; ``str.'' abbreviates ``strongly.'' All approximation ratios are with respect to the expected makespan objective.}}{29}{table.caption.7}%
